   Physical Therapy Faculty Practice     View Menu  Down arrow icon                 Due to the COVID-19 pandemic we are currently offering telehealth services to patients who may be in need of physical therapy. Please contact us at 312.413.8043 to schedule a telehealth visit. In-person physical therapy sessions are being scheduled on a case by case basis only at this time. For questions related to Cardiac Rehabilitation or nutritional services please call 312.324.4247. If you have an urgent exercise testing need, please speak directly with your provider. We look forward to returning to normal operations in the future.      Offering expert consultations, evaluations and interventions     At UIC’s Physical Therapy Faculty Practice, we’re committed to providing a truly exceptional experience for all patients who entrust us with their care.  We know that all of our patients are unique, so we tailor our services to your individual goals. Our team is made up of multi-specialty, highly-skilled Physical Therapists, Clinical Exercise Physiologists and Dietitians who work to create an individualized treatment plan just for you.  We’re embedded in the Chicago community, providing high-quality physical therapy, dietary and cardiac services in a convenient location, and we make coming to see us as easy as possible. We look forward to working with you to improve your health!            They really care about helping you get back into shape and in control of your life   A PT Faculty Practice client        What we can do for you     If aches and pains are preventing you from doing what’s important to you, we’re here to address the problem and make sure you know how to avoid it in the future. If you want to get back to your team—on the field, in the office, or at home—we’ll help you reach your goal.             Physical Therapy   Restore and maintain optimal physical function            Cardiac Rehabilitation   Improve your physical fitness and health through exercise training and lifestyle change            Cardiopulmonary Exercise Stress Testing   Measure how well your body responds to exercise and assess your fitness               The staff was great and my therapist provided excellent care. I can't say enough good things about the services I received!   A PT Faculty Practice client        Research and education   As part of UIC’s College of Applied Health Sciences, we partner with other innovative research centers and renowned leaders in the field. This helps us bring you services that are based on the very latest in research and best practices.  We are also active in training the next generation of physical therapists, working with the UIC Department of Physical Therapy to provide a residency program in orthopedic physical therapy .      Our team            Aaron Keil  Director      Meet Aaron              Brian Baranyi  Physical Therapist      Meet Brian              Deborah Davey  Physical Therapist      Meet Deborah              Shayna Oshita  Registered Dietitian and Certified Diabetes Educator      Meet Shayna              Cemal Ozemek  Director, Cardiac Rehabilitation Program      Meet Cemal              Hannah C. Ozemek  Clinical Exercise Physiologist Director, Cardiopulmonary Exercise Stress Testing      Meet Hannah              Manshi Patel  Clinical Exercise Physiologist      Meet Manshi              Justin Payette  Physical Therapist      Meet Justin              Adam Wielechowski  Physical Therapist      Meet Adam                      Come see us  1640 W. Roosevelt Rd. DHSP 338 Chicago, IL 60608 Phone: (312) 413-8043 Fax: (312) 413-8333  Hours  Monday – Thursday : 7 a.m. – 6 p.m.  Friday : 7 a.m. – 4:30 p.m.  Saturday and Sunday: Closed              Physical Therapy Faculty Practice    Back to main content           Physical Therapy    Cardiac Rehabilitation    Cardiopulmonary Exercise Stress Testing    Orthopedic Physical Therapy Residency Program    Sports Physical Therapy Residency Program    Directory    Contact           